<script>
  var name = '{{customer.first_name}} {{customer.last_name}}';
  var email = '{{customer.email}}';
 
window.LOQ = window.LOQ || [];
window.LOQ.push(['ready', async LO => {
    await LO.$internal.ready('visitor');
    LO.visitor.identify(name, { email: email });
}]);
</script>
